    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Is ElevenLabs free?</h3>
    <p>Yes. ElevenLabs offers a free plan with 10,000 characters per month. No credit card required. It includes access to all basic voices and the text-to-speech feature.</p>

    <h3>Can ElevenLabs clone any voice?</h3>
    <p>Yes, but you need at least 1 minute of clean audio from the person whose voice you want to clone. ElevenLabs requires consent verification — you must confirm you have permission to use the voice.</p>

    <h3>How many languages does ElevenLabs support?</h3>
    <p>ElevenLabs supports 29 languages including English, Spanish, French, German, Portuguese, Hindi, Japanese, Korean, Arabic, and more. Quality varies by language — English is the best.</p>

    <h3>Is ElevenLabs better than Murf AI?</h3>
    <p>For voice quality, yes. ElevenLabs produces more natural, human-like voices. However, Murf AI has a better built-in video editor and is easier for beginners. See our full <a href="/comparisons">comparison</a>.</p>

    <h3>Can I use ElevenLabs for commercial purposes?</h3>
    <p>Yes, on paid plans. The free plan is for personal/testing use only. Paid plans include commercial rights for all generated audio.</p>

